From f48b54bf2c42cf565504a4f6db4bcd6d41eb5c5a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Raja Ramkaran Reddy Rudravaram <ramkaran@rcvinnovations.com>
Date: Thu, 19 Mar 2026 05:12:48 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Fix edge-to-edge: replace deprecated
 statusBarColor/navigationBarColor with enableEdgeToEdge() +
 WindowInsetsCompat

- Remove android:statusBarColor and android:navigationBarColor from both themes.xml
  (deprecated and ignored on API 35+)
- Add enableEdgeToEdge() call before super.onCreate() in all 3 Activities
- Add ViewCompat.setOnApplyWindowInsetsListener for proper system bar inset handling
- Add androidx.core:core-ktx 1.15.0 dependency for WindowInsetsCompat APIs
- Bump versionCode to 2, versionName to 1.1.0

Resolves Play Console warnings:
  - "Edge-to-edge may not display for all users"
  - "Your app uses deprecated APIs or parameters for edge-to-edge"

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 app/build.gradle.kts                          |  5 ++--
 .../ui/dashboard/DashboardActivity.kt         | 18 ++++++++++++
 .../calendar/ui/detail/EventDetailActivity.kt | 29 +++++++++++++++----
 .../calendar/ui/signin/SignInActivity.kt      | 17 +++++++++++
 app/src/main/res/values-night/themes.xml      |  4 +--
 app/src/main/res/values/themes.xml            |  4 +--
 gradle/libs.versions.toml                     |  2 ++
 7 files changed, 67 insertions(+), 12 deletions(-)

